132
00:08:22,470 --> 00:08:25,390
- It was super delicious, right? 
 - Yeah, it was.

133
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:28,690
Man, I had so much fun.

134
00:08:28,690 --> 00:08:30,430
Me too.

135
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:32,690
Wanna take a bath together when we get home?

136
00:08:32,690 --> 00:08:34,630
