149
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:45,450
Yeah, sure.

150
00:09:45,450 --> 00:09:47,720
Sorry for interrupting whatever you were doing.

151
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,010
I'll sleep in my own room, after all.

152
00:09:49,010 --> 00:09:52,290
Hang on. I think there's been a misunderstanding.

153
00:09:52,290 --> 00:09:53,790
You were watching porn, weren't you?

154
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:55,850
I was not.

155
00:09:57,420 --> 00:10:00,910
Come on in. Lie down with me.

156
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:03,840
Don't look at me like that.

157
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:06,320
Here. In you go.

158
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:09,450
- Make yourself comfy. 
 - Thanks.

159
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:15,310
Your feet are cold.

160
00:10:15,310 --> 00:10:18,930
Today feels colder than usual.

161
00:10:20,690 --> 00:10:24,030
Did you come into my room to warm yourself up?

162
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:29,440
Come here.

163
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:34,750
- Warm your feet under mine. 
 - Wow, they're so warm.

164
00:10:43,230 --> 00:10:45,330
Hijiri, what are you doing?

165
00:10:46,450 --> 00:10:48,070
Sorry, nothing in particular.

166
00:10:48,070 --> 00:10:51,950
Not that it's nothing, I just thought that your hand felt cold.

167
00:10:51,950 --> 00:10:53,860
I-Is it?

168
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:56,590
 Hijiri has been acting strange lately. 

169
00:10:56,590 --> 00:10:58,770
What should we eat for dinner tonight?

170
00:10:58,770 --> 00:11:02,860
 Even when we're together, he's often distracted. 

171
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:07,540
Are you listening?

172
00:11:09,250 --> 00:11:10,850
Of course.

173
00:11:11,690 --> 00:11:15,650
