183
00:11:53,990 --> 00:11:57,200
- Hello? Hoshi? 
 - No, impossible!

184
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:59,900
- What now? 
  - Hijiri would never cheat on me. 

185
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:01,690
 And if he did, he's serious about her. 

186
00:12:01,690 --> 00:12:03,480
No, I can't think that way!

187
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,620
What on earth is wrong with you?

188
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:09,000
 No, I can't let it keep bugging me. 

189
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,600
 I'll just ask him directly. Calm down, calm down... 

190
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:15,640
I need to ask you something, too, Kihara. Can we discuss it during lunchtime?

191
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:16,890
- Nope. 
 - Why not?

192
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:19,580
- Our precious lunch time, our freedom. 
 - I agree.

193
00:12:19,580 --> 00:12:21,840
