195
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:27,080
Enomoto, you're a good man!

196
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:30,400
- Sorry, could you get out of the way? 
 - Oops, sorry.

197
00:12:32,490 --> 00:12:36,020
 But when should I pop the question? 

198
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:41,430
 I don't want him to feel like I don't trust him. 

199
00:12:41,430 --> 00:12:44,260
Koyori, we need to talk.

200
00:12:44,260 --> 00:12:46,210
Sorry to scare you. Are you okay?

201
00:12:46,210 --> 00:12:47,980
I'm fine.

202
00:12:51,610 --> 00:12:53,700
What is it?

203
