You see...

204
00:13:03,820 --> 00:13:08,250
 Don't tell me he really has someone else, and wants to break up? 

205
00:13:09,860 --> 00:13:11,670
- I don't want to break up! 
 - About the birthday...

206
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:13,040
- Huh? 
 - Huh?

207
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:17,600
Break up? Why?

208
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:24,510
- I don't want to break up. 
 - Birthday?

209
00:13:24,510 --> 00:13:28,020
- Whose birthday? 
 - Yours.

210
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:32,220
- Oh, I forgot about that! 
 - How could you forget?

211
00:13:32,220 --> 00:13:35,980
And what's all this about breaking up?

212
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:41,940
