221
00:14:17,130 --> 00:14:21,010
- So I thought... 
 - You thought?

222
00:14:21,010 --> 00:14:23,280
No, it's nothing.

223
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:26,490
 Sorry for not trusting you, Hijiri. 

224
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:31,980
This Saturday, let's go shop for your present,

225
00:14:31,980 --> 00:14:34,960
